nderline">技</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline"> 有 限 公 司</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:54.4pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:none">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:54.4pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:新宋体; font-size:12pt">通讯地址：  </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">广 州 市 花 都 区 云 山 大 道 44 号</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">              </span><span style="font-family:新宋体; font-size:12pt">      </span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-indent:54.4pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:新宋体; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">电话：      </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">18148924118                    刘幼明</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:31.5pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">为补充甲方寒假期间人力激增之需求,甲乙双方经友好协商，就乙方向甲方提供实习生输送事宜，双方自愿达成如下协议。</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">一、</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">合同期限：</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">    合同期自</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">       </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">年</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">   </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">月</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">    </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">日至</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">       </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">年</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">   </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">月</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">    </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">日止。</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">二、</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">学员的输送：</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">  1、乙方根据甲方要求组织</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">   汽车相关专业学生  </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">到甲方门店实训实习工作，工作岗位定性为</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline"> 汽车美容、快修、保养  </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">等专业对口岗位。 </span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">  2、乙方输送至甲方的汽车相关专业实习生必须年满</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline"> 16 </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">周</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">岁，</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline"> 25</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">周岁以下</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">，会说普通话，无残疾。</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">  3、实习生因个人原因需要提前结束服务期的，应提前3天向甲、乙双方同时提出申请，甲方依法办理移交手续后，其相关工资和劳动合同解除手续由乙方负责办理，甲方提供协助。</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">三、</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">工作时间及薪资待遇</span><span style="width:10.5pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">  1、</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">实习生工作时间：具体上班工作时间参照甲方作息制度。如有延时，参照甲方同岗位员工标准给予延时津贴。</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">  2、福利待遇： 100元/人/天，人走账清。</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">  3、膳食和住宿：甲方为乙方之学员提供免费食宿。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">  4、</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">结算时间和方式：</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">实习生的薪资补贴均由门店在学生离职后</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">个工作日内统一转入乙方指定账户：户名</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">:</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">__</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">刘幼明</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">__</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">  </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">账号：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">__6217003320025669402___</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">开户银行：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">___</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">中国建设银行广州天贵支行</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">_</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">【转账请备注门店名称】。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">四、双方的权利和义务：</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">（一） 甲方：</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="width:21pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:normal">、甲方提供学员的实习岗位和相关设备，并向学员提供符合国家安全卫生标准的实习环境</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:normal">。因甲方</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:normal">提供不符合国家安全卫生标准的实习环境所造成的一切后果由甲方承担。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="width:21pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">2、</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">学员在使用甲方的机器设备时，甲方必须提前进行安全生产操作规程的上岗培训，待学员通过甲方考核合格后，才能上机操作；操作过程中必须遵守有关安全生产操作规程。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="width:21pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:normal">3、在实习过程中，如发生学员不遵守甲方的各项规章制度，不胜任实习工作或不服从甲方工作安排，或经甲方考核不合格的情况，</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:normal"> 甲方可以提3天通知乙方退回该学员。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; padding-left:20.7pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-20.7pt"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">   </span><span style="width:4.95pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt"> </span><span style="width:16.7pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">4、实习期间甲方</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">作为投保人为实习生办理实习生意外伤害保险，且担负</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">学员在甲方管理区域内的人身安全和意外责任。</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">                            </span></p><p style="line-height:25pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">     </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">（二） 乙方：</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:15.75pt"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="width:11.25pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">1、乙方应向甲方提供学员名单及身份证复印件等甲方要求的文件。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0.85pt"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">　</span><span style="width:10.5pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">2、乙方委派专人负责对学员进行协助管理，并对学员进行生活督导与和日常生活安全管理。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">  </span><span style="width:10.5pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">3、学员从学校到达甲方及离开甲方返校途中，期间的安全责任由乙方负责。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:15.75pt"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="width:11.25pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">4、按照国家及地方法规及甲方要求及时与学员办理相关实习手续、后勤服务等。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">　    </span><span style="width:16.5pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">5、做好协调工作，分别向甲方及学员双向反馈合理意见并协助解决。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">五、协议的变更、终止、解除和生效</span></p><p style="line-height:20pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="width:21pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">1、本协议书未尽事宜，双方另行协商并签署补充协议，作为本协议的附件，具有同等法律效力。本协议条款与现行劳动法律法规规定有出入的，按现行劳动法律法规规定执行。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:125%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="width:18pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block; -aw-tabstop-align:left; -aw-tabstop-pos:18pt"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">2、本协议一式两份,甲乙双方各执壹份,经双方签字并加盖单位公章之日起生效，至协议终止之日失效。</span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 10pt 10pt 0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0.95pt"><span style="width:21pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">3、当甲乙双方因本协议的履行发生争议时,应力争友好协商解决,当无法解决时,向</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">广州花都人民法院起诉。</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt"> </span></p><p style="line-height:21pt; margin:0pt 10pt 10pt 0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0.95pt"><span style="width:21pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block"></span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">4、</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">甲、乙双方在平等友好的基础上签订本协议，未尽的条款双方可以签署《</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">补充协议</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">》的形式为补充，该《</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">补充协议</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">》与本协议具有同等的法律效力。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:32.35pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">甲方（盖章）：</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:none">                              </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">     乙方（盖章）</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">：</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; text-decoration:underline">                          </span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:32.35pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">代表签名：                                      代表签名：</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:32.35pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt">日期：    年   月   日                          日期：     年    月   日</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div><div class="cnzz" style="di